  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Multi-Tool</span>. This rifle's <span class=\"name name-technology\">Blaze Javelin</span> delivers precise, powerful beams of energy to long-range targets, both <span class=\"name name-stellar\">damaging</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">stunning</span> them.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Take</span> this Multi-Tool to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current Multi-Tool. Swap between active Multi-Tools from the Utilities section of the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一台专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">多用途工具</span>。这把步枪的<span class=\"name name-technology\">火焰标枪</span>能够发射威力强大而且精准的能量光束，<span class=\"name name-stellar\">伤害</span>并<span class=\"name name-stellar\">击晕</span>远距离目标。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收下</span>这个多用途工具，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的多用途工具<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中的工具部分切换可用的多用途工具。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">工具組</span>。這把步槍的<span class=\"name name-technology\">火焰標槍</span>能夠對遠距離目標發射精準、強大的能量光束，對目標造成<span class=\"name name-stellar\">傷害</span>，並<span class=\"name name-stellar\">擊暈</span>目標。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">取走</span>這個工具組加入你的收藏，或是與目前工具組<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 中的機能選項切換使用中的工具組。"
  },
